\par "I never dropped anything in your study. That's not mine. That's Anne's."
\par "I know that," I said.
\par "Well, why ask me, then? Anne must have dropped it."
\par "Mrs. Protheroe has only been in my study once since the murder, and then she was wearing black and so would not have been likely to have had on a blue ear\_ring."
